{"tid":245432,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如何放低一個人","createTime":"2017-05-16T08:47:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-16T22:55:42.000Z","uid":117176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ebfbd119af0bf0a9c41a0117a7c69cfe4c23073a","tid":245432,"uid":117176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T08:47:45.000Z","msg":"同前女散左兩個月 重未放得低佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依加有條女冧我 啲豬朋狗友叫我受左佢<br />\n但係我未放低上一段感情 唔想將佢當水泡<br />\n你地話應該受/唔受？"},{"pid":"5a9251ac1ddc1ba53dd0de80c882b8f8d1326851","tid":245432,"uid":114518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T09:27:37.000Z","msg":"唔好當人水泡<br />\n如果你投入到呢段新既感情既都仲好<br />\n最怕投入唔到 害左人 浪費人地時間<br />\n結果你自己都兩頭唔到岸吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4cabd8b5772fee97f079a0cbfd57e4d6f2d9318","tid":245432,"uid":96979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T21:34:27.000Z","msg":"唔受<br />\n<br />\n到你真正有返感覺先再拍拖<br />\n唔好一時之快傷害一個人<br />\n<br />\n人生流流長怕咩冇機會"},{"pid":"680dbea81ad9ab2e78651d38a9a14a47dfc36d38","tid":245432,"uid":8867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T21:49:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3dea1af7e884944f212ce502b2669b3d6f1ad9bb","tid":245432,"uid":50969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T22:55:42.000Z","msg":"我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你識唔識呀？<br />\n識既唔好收埋教下我呀"}]}